---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="AI Consulting – Jacob Marriott"
  description="I set up personalised AI systems for professionals and businesses across Australia and New Zealand. Claude Code environments, custom skills, knowledge graphs, automation workflows."
>
  <section class="consult-section container">
    <p class="section-label">
      <span aria-hidden="true">01 / </span>what i do
    </p>
    <div class="consult-body">
      <p>
        I build personalised AI systems for professionals and business owners – structured
        setups that know your work, your clients, and how you operate. Not just a chat window.
        A real working layer on top of your day.
      </p>
      <p>
        This means a Claude Code environment built around you: a profile that persists across
        every session, custom shortcuts for the tasks you repeat, a knowledge graph that maps
        your documents and finds connections, and an automation roadmap for what to tackle next.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="consult-section container">
    <p class="section-label">
      <span aria-hidden="true">02 / </span>who it's for
    </p>
    <div class="consult-body">
      <p>
        Professionals who spend too much time on things that should be faster – drafting,
        summarising, researching, preparing. Solo operators and small teams. People who've
        used ChatGPT through a browser and want something that actually knows them.
      </p>
      <p>
        Current clients include a barrister and a travel industry consultant. I work with
        clients across Australia and New Zealand.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="consult-section container">
    <p class="section-label">
      <span aria-hidden="true">03 / </span>how it works
    </p>
    <div class="consult-body">
      <ol class="consult-steps">
        <li class="consult-step">
          <span class="consult-step__num mono">01</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Context</strong> – before anything gets built, I need to understand how you
            actually work. Your tools, your clients, your recurring tasks, the documents you
            keep going back to. The whole point of a personalised AI setup is that it knows
            you – so this is where that starts.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="consult-step">
          <span class="consult-step__num mono">02</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Build</strong> – one focused session where I set up your full AI environment:
            profile, rules, skills, knowledge graph. You leave with a working system.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="consult-step">
          <span class="consult-step__num mono">03</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Check-in</strong> – one week later I review what you've actually used, tune
            what isn't working, and add anything that emerged.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="consult-step">
          <span class="consult-step__num mono">04</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Ongoing</strong> – monthly support, new skills as your work
            evolves, graph updates, advanced automations.
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="consult-section container">
    <p class="section-label">
      <span aria-hidden="true">04 / </span>get in touch
    </p>
    <div class="consult-body">
      <p>
        If this sounds relevant, email me at
        <a href="mailto:hello@jacobmarriott.com">hello@jacobmarriott.com</a>
        or use the contact form on the main site. Happy to have a quick call first.
      </p>
      <p class="consult-back">
        <a href="/">← jacobmarriott.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .consult-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-section);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .consult-section:first-child {
    border-top: 0;
    padding-top: clamp(6rem, 4rem + 10vw, 12rem);
  }

  .consult-body {
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 48rem) {
    .consult-section {
      grid-template-columns: 10rem minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-8) clamp(1.5rem, -1rem + 8vw, 5rem);
      align-items: start;
    }

    .consult-body {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      line-height: var(--leading-prose);
    }
  }

  .consult-steps {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .consult-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.5rem minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .consult-step__num {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    padding-top: 0.25em;
  }

  .consult-back {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
  }

  .consult-back a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    border-bottom: 0;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .consult-back a:hover,
  .consult-back a:focus-visible {
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
